title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1991-09-14
lineage: (DAT master) Sony D8 -> Oade 7-pin/Coax -> Tascam HD-P2 -> wav -> Sound Studio -> xACT -> flac (16/48); recorded by: Dan O'Neill, FOB/DFC
description:
Set 1

Let The Good Times Roll, Jack Straw, Friend Of The Devil, Little Red Rooster, Jack A Roe, Desolation Row, Tennessee Jed, Promised Land

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Ship of Fools-> Truckin'-> Jam-> Spoonful-> He's Gone, Drums-> Jam-> All Along The Watchtower, China Doll-> One More Saturday Night, E: The Weight
